title: Uncubicled Part 2
description: This is not a sequel to Uncubicled, it is the second half of the original story. If you purchased Uncubicled before 11/15/2010, you've already read this part.If you aren't sure if you've read this or not, please download the free sample before purchasing.Like Uncubicled on Facebook for the latest sequel news.
author: Josh McMains
